| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0257 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9c77af1c-5fc4-5021-8280-0d657ac7b9f3"
